  fhir:description [ fhir:v "Concepts for non-bleeding signs and symptoms often associated with colorectal cancer. Includes diarrhea, constipation, tenesmus, abdominal pain or cramping, fatigue or weakness, unintended or unexplained weight loss, change in bowel habits or stool shape."] ; # 
